Second Department,

October, 1956

(October 1, 1956) In the Matter of Criterion Porter & Window Cleaning Service Corporation, Petitioner, against Supreme Court of the State of New York, County of Kings, et al., Respondents.

Application by respondents, pursuant to section 1293 of the Civil Practice Act to dismiss the petition granted, with $10 costs and disbursements. The petition does not state facts sufficient to justify the granting of the relief sought. Present —Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Murphy and Hallinan, JJ.
